1
00:01:28,858 --> 00:01:32,558
KIRARA, DOES IT HURT?
[WHIMPERING]

2
00:01:32,592 --> 00:01:37,325
NARAKU'S POISONS ARE STILL
IN YOUR SYSTEM.

3
00:01:39,358 --> 00:01:40,392
AN HERBAL ANTIDOTE?

4
00:01:40,425 --> 00:01:42,958
DOES THAT MEAN THERE'S A CURE
FOR KIRARA'S SICKNESS?

5
00:01:42,992 --> 00:01:47,158
- HMM.
I HAVE HEARD RUMORS
OF AN HERB GARDEN

6
00:01:47,192 --> 00:01:48,258
NOT FAR FROM HERE.

7
00:01:48,292 --> 00:01:49,958
UNFORTUNATELY FOR US,

8
00:01:49,992 --> 00:01:52,858
THERE'S ALSO A RUMOR
ABOUT A DEMON.

9
00:01:52,892 --> 00:01:55,792
- BUT THAT'S A PERFECT JOB
FOR INUYASHA.

10
00:01:55,825 --> 00:01:57,025
AFTER HE BEATS THE DEMON,

11
00:01:57,058 --> 00:01:58,758
THEN WE CAN TAKE
WHATEVER WE NEED.

12
00:01:58,792 --> 00:02:01,192
- HA. WELL, IF IT HELPS
KIRARA HERE,

13
00:02:01,225 --> 00:02:02,125
I'M HAPPY TO DO IT.

14
00:02:02,158 --> 00:02:05,358
SHE ACTUALLY HELPS IN BATTLE,
UNLIKE MYOGA.

15
00:02:05,392 --> 00:02:06,125
[SPUTTERING]

16
00:02:06,158 --> 00:02:07,792
- WE CAN ACTUALLY
COUNT ON KIRARA.

17
00:02:07,825 --> 00:02:09,858
UNLIKE SOME PEOPLE,
WITHOUT HER STRENGTH,

18
00:02:09,892 --> 00:02:13,025
WE COULD REALLY BE IN TROUBLE.
- MM-HMM.
[SPUTTERING]

19
00:02:13,058 --> 00:02:15,525
- COME ON, YOU GUYS.
YOU'RE BEING UNFAIR.

20
00:02:15,558 --> 00:02:17,158
MYOGA'S BEEN A BIG HELP TO US.

21
00:02:17,192 --> 00:02:19,392
DON'T YOU REMEMBER
THAT TIME THAT HE--

22
00:02:19,425 --> 00:02:21,658
THAT HE, UH--
UH, THAT HE, UH...

23
00:02:21,692 --> 00:02:26,758
- OOH...OK! OK!
ENOUGH WITH
THE FAINT PRAISE ALREADY!

24
00:02:26,792 --> 00:02:29,558
WHAT'S A FLEA GOTTA DO
TO CATCH A BREAK AROUND HERE?

25
00:02:29,592 --> 00:02:31,425
YOU ACT LIKE SIZE IS EVERYTHING.

26
00:02:31,458 --> 00:02:34,125
WELL, IT ISN'T!
BRAINS COUNT, TOO, YOU KNOW!

27
00:02:34,158 --> 00:02:36,025
OH, COME ON, ADMIT IT!
ADMIT IT!

28
00:02:36,058 --> 00:02:39,925
- SO THEY WENT TO FIND MEDICINE,
DID THEY?

29
00:02:39,958 --> 00:02:41,992
INUYASHA AND THE OTHERS?

30
00:02:42,025 --> 00:02:44,458
- YES, THEY DID,
AND I'VE STAYED BACK HERE

31
00:02:44,492 --> 00:02:45,458
TO PROTECT AND LOOK AFTER YOU,

32
00:02:45,492 --> 00:02:50,158
SO, NO MORE TALKING,
AND TRY AND GET SOME REST.

33
00:02:51,892 --> 00:02:55,692
SOMETHING WRONG?
- IT MIGHT BE SAFER OUTSIDE.

34
00:02:55,725 --> 00:02:57,458
- AND THAT'S WHY KAGOME SENT ME,

35
00:02:57,492 --> 00:03:01,392
SO THAT I COULD PROTECT YOU
FROM BEING PROTECTED BY HIM.

36
00:03:01,425 --> 00:03:03,592
- WHAT HE SAID.

37
00:03:04,425 --> 00:03:06,225
[GROAN]

38
00:03:11,592 --> 00:03:14,225
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

39
00:03:20,158 --> 00:03:24,758
[GROAN]
- IT WOULD BE FASTER
IF I WENT BY MYSELF.

40
00:03:24,792 --> 00:03:26,792
- LET'S SAY YOU COULD
GET THERE FASTER.

41
00:03:26,825 --> 00:03:28,492
WHAT WOULD YOU DO
ONCE YOU GOT THERE, THOUGH?

42
00:03:28,525 --> 00:03:31,892
COULD YOU TELL THE GOOD HERBS
FROM THE BAD?
I DON'T THINK SO.

43
00:03:31,925 --> 00:03:35,392
AFTER ALL, KAEDE DID TEACH ME
ALL ABOUT THEM.

44
00:03:35,425 --> 00:03:37,458
- YEAH. OK.
WHATEVER.

45
00:03:37,492 --> 00:03:41,958
- AND IT'LL BE REALLY NICE
TO SPEND TIME TOGETHER.
DON'T YOU THINK?

46
00:03:41,992 --> 00:03:45,758
AT FIRST, IT WAS JUST US
LOOKING FOR THE JEWEL,

47
00:03:45,792 --> 00:03:47,092
BUT NOW WE HAVE HELP!

48
00:03:47,125 --> 00:03:50,425
FIGHTING DEMONS ALL THE TIME
IS NOT EASY, YOU KNOW?

49
00:03:50,458 --> 00:03:54,492
WE COULDN'T DO IT WITHOUT
OR FRIENDS, COULD WE, NOW?

50
00:03:54,525 --> 00:03:56,025
HMM?
OH.

51
00:03:56,058 --> 00:03:59,658
HE'S ASLEEP.
MUST BE TIRED.

52
00:03:59,692 --> 00:04:03,825
I GUESS HE WOULD BE,
WITH THAT FIGHT WITH NARAKU.

53
00:04:03,858 --> 00:04:05,192
HE MUST'VE REALLY WORN HIM OUT.

54
00:04:05,225 --> 00:04:10,025
IF I'M QUIET, THOUGH,
HE WON'T WAKE UP.

55
00:04:11,025 --> 00:04:13,558
QUIET.
QUIET.

56
00:04:13,592 --> 00:04:14,425
- HELLO!

57
00:04:14,458 --> 00:04:17,325
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

58
00:04:17,358 --> 00:04:20,092
- OH, OH, OH...

59
00:04:20,125 --> 00:04:22,825
[BREATHING HEAVILY]
OH, OH...

60
00:04:23,825 --> 00:04:25,258
OH!

61
00:04:26,292 --> 00:04:30,025
AAH!

62
00:04:33,192 --> 00:04:34,158
- COME ON.

63
00:04:34,192 --> 00:04:36,692
YOU'RE NOT STILL MAD
ABOUT THE BIKE, ARE YOU?

64
00:04:36,725 --> 00:04:37,892
I SAID I WAS SORRY.

65
00:04:37,925 --> 00:04:42,692
- LOOK, I'M NOT MAD, OK?
I'M NOT.
REALLY.

66
00:04:43,525 --> 00:04:46,658
NOW WHAT?
- YOU LIKE SPENDING TIME
WITH ME, RIGHT?

67
00:04:46,692 --> 00:04:48,792
- DEPENDS.
IS IT A TRICK QUESTION?

68
00:04:48,825 --> 00:04:52,625
- OH, NEVER MIND.
I KNOW THE ANSWER.

69
00:04:53,892 --> 00:04:56,825
- EXCUSE ME,
DID I MISS SOMETHING?

70
00:04:56,858 --> 00:05:01,325
- HE ALWAYS RUINS EVERYTHING!

71
00:05:02,225 --> 00:05:02,925
HMM?

72
00:05:02,958 --> 00:05:05,592
UH, WHAT'S THAT?

73
00:05:05,625 --> 00:05:06,758
- WHAT'S WHAT?

74
00:05:06,792 --> 00:05:08,192
- THIRD ONE THIS WEEK.

75
00:05:08,225 --> 00:05:09,958
- I TELL YOU, IT'S JINENJI.

76
00:05:09,992 --> 00:05:13,925
- OF COURSE IT IS.
WHO ELSE WOULD IT BE
BUT THAT DEMON?

77
00:05:13,958 --> 00:05:17,492
- WHAT DO WE DO?
- YEAH, WHAT?

78
00:05:20,625 --> 00:05:23,025
- SO WHO'S JINENJI?
SOME KIND OF DEMON?

79
00:05:23,058 --> 00:05:25,525
- WHY SHOULD WE TELL YOU?
- ANOTHER DEMON!

80
00:05:25,558 --> 00:05:28,425
- HE IS, BUT HE'S NOT REALLY
A DEMON DEMON,

81
00:05:28,458 --> 00:05:30,525
IF YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN.
HEH.

82
00:05:30,558 --> 00:05:31,392
- OHH!

83
00:05:31,425 --> 00:05:33,592
- OH, WAIT!
THAT DIDN'T COME OUT RIGHT.

84
00:05:33,625 --> 00:05:34,625
WE'RE JUST TRYING TO FIND A FARM

85
00:05:34,658 --> 00:05:37,492
WHERE WE CAN FIND
A MEDICINAL HERB FOR OUR FRIEND.

86
00:05:37,525 --> 00:05:40,125
- WHAT HERB?
- YOU MEAN JINENJI, THEN.

87
00:05:40,158 --> 00:05:44,792
- JINENJI'S THE ONE
WHAT KILLED THIS POOR WOMAN.
- HUH?

88
00:05:44,825 --> 00:05:45,992
- YOU WANT JINENJI.

89
00:05:46,025 --> 00:05:49,525
BIG MONSTER WHO LIVES
EDGE OF THE VILLAGE
WITH HIS MOTHER.

90
00:05:49,558 --> 00:05:51,492
- THEM PLANTS OF HIS
WORK SURE ENOUGH,

91
00:05:51,525 --> 00:05:53,392
BUT LATELY, I--
THAT IS TO SAY, HE--

92
00:05:53,425 --> 00:05:59,525
- LATELY, HE'S GOT HIMSELF
A TASTE FOR HUMAN FLESH,
IS WHAT IT IS.

93
00:06:04,225 --> 00:06:05,058
[GROANING]

94
00:06:05,370 --> 00:06:09,736
THAT'S HIM THERE.
BIG FELLER, AIN'T HE?

95
00:06:09,770 --> 00:06:13,103
[GROANING]
- HUH. HE AIN'T SO BIG.

96
00:06:13,136 --> 00:06:16,403
- DON'T GO MAKING US NO PROMISES
YOU CAN'T KEEP, NOW.

97
00:06:16,436 --> 00:06:19,036
- I'M DOING IT FOR THE HERB,
NOT YOU.

98
00:06:19,070 --> 00:06:22,370
KAGOME, YOU STAY HERE.
- OK.

99
00:06:22,570 --> 00:06:25,103
- YOU RECKON HE'S STRONG ENOUGH?

100
00:06:25,136 --> 00:06:27,170
- DON'T REALLY MATTER NOW,
DO IT?

101
00:06:27,203 --> 00:06:28,236
AIN'T OUR PROBLEM NO MORE.

102
00:06:28,270 --> 00:06:31,603
- IF WE'RE LUCKY,
MAYBE THEY'LL KILL EACH OTHER.

103
00:06:31,636 --> 00:06:34,036
- OH, BOY.

104
00:06:34,336 --> 00:06:36,070
- UHH.
WHAT'S THE MATTER?

105
00:06:36,103 --> 00:06:36,970
DIDN'T YOUR MOTHER EVER TELL YOU

106
00:06:37,003 --> 00:06:39,470
NOT TO EAT PEOPLE
SMALLER THAN YOU?

107
00:06:39,503 --> 00:06:40,936
UHH!

108
00:06:42,203 --> 00:06:43,303
- HMM?

109
00:06:43,336 --> 00:06:44,836
- HUH?
THAT'S WEIRD.

110
00:06:44,870 --> 00:06:48,070
I HAVEN'T SEEN ANY
HUMAN BLOOD ON HIM.

111
00:06:48,103 --> 00:06:50,070
[GROANING]
- OW!

112
00:06:50,103 --> 00:06:53,370
- GO ON!
GET!
GET OUT OF HERE!

113
00:06:53,403 --> 00:06:56,603
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

114
00:06:56,636 --> 00:06:58,170
[THUNDER]

115
00:07:00,370 --> 00:07:02,370
[ROARING]

116
00:07:02,403 --> 00:07:03,770
[GROANING]

117
00:07:03,803 --> 00:07:06,303
- HUH?
HEY! WAIT!

118
00:07:06,336 --> 00:07:08,836
- MOM!
HELP!

119
00:07:08,870 --> 00:07:09,803
- WHY, YOU!

120
00:07:09,836 --> 00:07:10,670
- MOUNTAIN WITCH!

121
00:07:10,703 --> 00:07:12,470
- TRYING TO TAKE OUR LAND

122
00:07:12,503 --> 00:07:15,736
FOR YOURSELF AGAIN, ARE YA?

123
00:07:15,770 --> 00:07:16,636
- UH...

124
00:07:16,670 --> 00:07:19,170
- WELL, SO MUCH FOR THAT PLAN.
- RUN AWAY!

125
00:07:19,203 --> 00:07:21,170
- RUN AWAY!
[SCREAMING]

126
00:07:21,203 --> 00:07:25,903
- NOW I KNOW I MISSED SOMETHING.
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

127
00:07:25,936 --> 00:07:28,303
- I DON'T KNOW WHO
PUT YOU UP TO IT,

128
00:07:28,336 --> 00:07:29,403
OR WHAT YA BEEN TOLD,

129
00:07:29,436 --> 00:07:31,570
BUT THIS BOY WOULD NEVER
EAT SOMEONE.

130
00:07:31,603 --> 00:07:34,370
YOU GOT THAT?
WHO HE IS DON'T MATTER,

131
00:07:34,403 --> 00:07:36,536
WHETHER HALF-DEMON OR NOT!

132
00:07:36,570 --> 00:07:38,836
- HALF-DEMON?

133
00:07:38,870 --> 00:07:41,436
[WHIMPERING]

134
00:07:51,136 --> 00:07:53,803
- INUYASHA, WASN'T IT?

135
00:07:53,836 --> 00:07:56,636
YOU'RE HALF-DEMON, TOO,
BUT YOU DON'T LOOK IT.

136
00:07:56,670 --> 00:07:58,903
- SO YOU CAN TELL, CAN YOU?

137
00:07:58,936 --> 00:08:00,670
- HALF-BREEDS ARE FUNNY
THAT WAY.

138
00:08:00,703 --> 00:08:02,903
FOR EACH ONE BORN PRETTY,
LIKE YOU,

139
00:08:02,936 --> 00:08:04,203
THERE'S ANOTHER BORN WHAT AIN'T.

140
00:08:04,236 --> 00:08:09,103
- HE'S CUTE, ALL RIGHT,
BUT ONLY IF YOU'RE INTO DOGS.
[GROANS]

141
00:08:09,136 --> 00:08:11,636
- JUST IMAGINE WHAT IT'S LIKE
FOR HIM.

142
00:08:11,670 --> 00:08:13,270
BEING HALF-DEMON
SHOULDN'T MATTER,

143
00:08:13,303 --> 00:08:16,103
BUT THOSE VILLAGERS, THEY--
THEY TREAT HIM LIKE HE'S

144
00:08:16,136 --> 00:08:18,970
SOME KIND OF MONSTER
OR SOMETHING.

145
00:08:19,003 --> 00:08:20,136
[GROANS]

146
00:08:20,170 --> 00:08:22,870
- SO YOU'RE SAYING
THEY BULLY HIM?

147
00:08:22,903 --> 00:08:25,670
- OH, TRYING TO KILL HIM,
MORE LIKE.

148
00:08:25,703 --> 00:08:29,770
- I'M SORRY, MA.
IF I WEREN'T LIKE THIS, I...

149
00:08:29,803 --> 00:08:34,903
- STOP THAT RIGHT NOW.
DON'T YOU APOLOGIZE
FOR BEING DIFFERENT.

150
00:08:34,936 --> 00:08:36,536
YOUR FATHER, HE WAS DIFFERENT,

151
00:08:36,570 --> 00:08:40,036
AND THAT NEVER MADE NO
NO-MIND TO ME.

152
00:08:40,570 --> 00:08:44,903
I'LL NEVER FORGET
HOW I HURT MY ANKLE
AND COULDN'T WALK,

153
00:08:44,936 --> 00:08:47,770
AND HOW IT WAS YOUR FATHER
WHO SAVED ME.

154
00:08:47,803 --> 00:08:52,970
OH...THE MAN I SAW,
HE WAS GLOWING,

155
00:08:53,003 --> 00:08:55,270
BUT I KNEW HE WEREN'T REAL.

156
00:08:55,303 --> 00:08:57,736
NO MAN IS THAT PERFECT.

157
00:08:57,770 --> 00:09:05,336
I LOVED HIM ANYWAY.
HIM AND HIS DEMON LIGHT.

158
00:09:08,303 --> 00:09:09,636
OH...

159
00:09:09,670 --> 00:09:10,570
- UH...
- WAIT.

160
00:09:10,603 --> 00:09:12,936
IF YOU'RE SAYING
THE FATHER WAS THE DEMON,

161
00:09:12,970 --> 00:09:15,670
THEN THE HUMAN PARENT WAS YOU?

162
00:09:15,703 --> 00:09:17,236
- WHAT DID YOU THINK I WAS?

163
00:09:17,270 --> 00:09:20,803
- I THOUGHT YOU WERE BABA YAGA!
UH--

164
00:09:20,836 --> 00:09:21,936
- FOR YOU, FRIEND.

165
00:09:21,970 --> 00:09:25,670
IT'S MEDICINE FOR THE FRIEND
YOU SAID GOT POISON IN HIM.

166
00:09:25,703 --> 00:09:29,370
- UH, OK.
UM, HOW MUCH?

167
00:09:29,403 --> 00:09:31,236
- NOTHING.
IT'S THE LEAST I CAN DO

168
00:09:31,270 --> 00:09:33,603
TO MAKE UP FOR THE CLUBBING
I GAVE EARLIER.

169
00:09:33,636 --> 00:09:36,436
NOW LEAVE,
BEFORE I GRIND YOUR BONES

170
00:09:36,470 --> 00:09:39,470
AND MAKE OUR BREAD.

171
00:09:42,836 --> 00:09:44,470
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

172
00:09:44,503 --> 00:09:46,870
- UM, UH...

173
00:09:47,503 --> 00:09:50,903
INUYASHA, SHOULDN'T WE
BE STAYING?
- SHOULD WE?

174
00:09:50,936 --> 00:09:54,503
- THE VILLAGERS.
THEY THINK JINENJI'S
BEEN EATING PEOPLE.

175
00:09:54,536 --> 00:09:56,070
YOU KNOW THEY DO.

176
00:09:56,103 --> 00:09:57,270
MAYBE HE IS DIFFERENT,

177
00:09:57,303 --> 00:09:59,503
BUT THAT DOESN'T MEAN
THAT HE'S GUILTY.

178
00:09:59,536 --> 00:10:02,070
- BUT THAT'S WHAT IT DOES MEAN
WHEN YOU'RE DIFFERENT.

179
00:10:02,103 --> 00:10:05,270
NOBODY TRUSTS YOU,
YOU'RE ALWAYS THE FIRST
TO BE BLAMED,

180
00:10:05,303 --> 00:10:09,436
AND IT IS ALWAYS,
ALWAYS YOUR FAULT!

181
00:10:13,236 --> 00:10:15,936
- GATHER EVERY SWORD,
EVERY SPEAR IN THE VILLAGE!

182
00:10:15,970 --> 00:10:20,270
- THIS IS PLENTY.
EVEN HE CAN'T TAKE ALL THESE.

183
00:10:20,303 --> 00:10:22,536
- TONIGHT'S GONNA BE THE NIGHT.

184
00:10:22,570 --> 00:10:24,970
IT'S KILL OR BE KILLED.

185
00:10:25,003 --> 00:10:25,836
- BUT IT'S NOT!

186
00:10:25,870 --> 00:10:27,570
- SO IT'S YOU TWO AGAIN.

187
00:10:27,603 --> 00:10:30,603
- YOU'RE NOT ATTACKING JINENJI,
ARE YOU?

188
00:10:30,636 --> 00:10:31,470
- OF COURSE WE ARE!

189
00:10:31,503 --> 00:10:33,303
- BUT--BUT YOU DON'T
HAVE ANY PROOF

190
00:10:33,336 --> 00:10:34,770
THAT HE WAS THE ONE WHO--

191
00:10:34,803 --> 00:10:36,603
- HOW CAN YOU BE SO NAIVE?

192
00:10:36,636 --> 00:10:39,936
- THEY HATE US,
THE WITCH AND HER MONSTER SON.

193
00:10:39,970 --> 00:10:42,170
- UH, COWARDS IS
WHAT THEY ARE.

194
00:10:42,203 --> 00:10:45,503
- INTERESTING,
BECAUSE THE WAY I SEE IT,

195
00:10:45,536 --> 00:10:47,236
IT'S THE OTHER WAY AROUND.

196
00:10:47,270 --> 00:10:48,036
- WHAT?

197
00:10:48,070 --> 00:10:49,270
- RIGHT NOW, THOUGH,

198
00:10:49,303 --> 00:10:51,003
WE GOT MORE IMPORTANT BUSINESS,

199
00:10:51,036 --> 00:10:53,403
LIKE CATCHING THE REAL
FLESH-EATER.

200
00:10:53,436 --> 00:10:55,936
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
"REAL FLESH-EATER"?

201
00:10:55,970 --> 00:10:58,170
YOU PLANNING ON CATCHING IT?

202
00:10:58,203 --> 00:11:00,636
- INUYASHA, I'M GOING BACK.

203
00:11:00,670 --> 00:11:01,503
- BACK WHERE?

204
00:11:01,536 --> 00:11:03,336
- I'M GOING TO BE OVER
AT JINENJI'S FARM,

205
00:11:03,370 --> 00:11:05,903
SO DON'T EVEN THINK ABOUT
ATTACKING THERE, OK?

206
00:11:05,936 --> 00:11:07,870
IF YOU HURT ME,
YOU'LL ALL HAVE TO DIE,

207
00:11:07,903 --> 00:11:11,036
BECAUSE INUYASHA HERE
WILL HAVE TO AVENGE ME.

208
00:11:11,070 --> 00:11:12,736
- I WILL?
SINCE WHEN?

209
00:11:12,770 --> 00:11:13,970
- YOU'D BETTER AVENGE ME.

210
00:11:14,003 --> 00:11:16,403
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED
TO DO IF YOU DON'T?

211
00:11:16,436 --> 00:11:17,870
- FINE.
I'LL AVENGE YOU ALREADY.

212
00:11:17,903 --> 00:11:22,836
- THINK WE CAN TRUST HIM?
- WOULDN'T HOLD MY BREATH.

213
00:11:27,170 --> 00:11:31,503
- THAT MURDERED WOMAN.
I COULD SMELL DEMON
ALL OVER HER.

214
00:11:31,536 --> 00:11:34,703
I SMELL IT NOW.
REALLY CLOSE.
YAA!

215
00:11:34,736 --> 00:11:37,136
- THEY DID, DID THEY?

216
00:11:37,170 --> 00:11:40,036
- YEAH, WHICH IS WHY I TOLD THEM
I'D BE STAYING HERE,

217
00:11:40,070 --> 00:11:43,870
TILL JINENJI COULD BE
PROVEN INNOCENT.

218
00:11:43,903 --> 00:11:45,803
- HAVE IT YOUR WAY.
UHH.

219
00:11:45,836 --> 00:11:52,003
- JUST PULL WEEDS, RIGHT?
- WELL, YEAH.

220
00:11:55,570 --> 00:11:58,003
- SO MANY SCARS.

221
00:11:58,036 --> 00:12:00,636
ALL FROM THE VILLAGERS, I BET.

222
00:12:00,670 --> 00:12:04,870
HAVEN'T YOU EVER WANTED
TO GO SOMEPLACE ELSE?

223
00:12:04,903 --> 00:12:07,136
- THIS PLACE IS BEST.
- HUH?

224
00:12:07,170 --> 00:12:11,370
- MY PA LEFT ME THIS FARM.
- OH.

225
00:12:12,636 --> 00:12:15,803
- I DID IT.
FOR THE FIRST TIME IN MY LIFE,

226
00:12:15,836 --> 00:12:19,236
I TALKED TO A GIRL
AND SHE DIDN'T SCREAM.

227
00:12:19,270 --> 00:12:22,103
[SCREAM]
- AAH!

228
00:12:22,136 --> 00:12:25,203
IT'S A WORM!

229
00:12:25,236 --> 00:12:26,803
THANK YOU.
[EXHALES]

230
00:12:26,836 --> 00:12:32,970
- HMM.
SHE'S SCARED OF A WORM,
BUT NOT OF JINENJI?

231
00:12:33,003 --> 00:12:35,636
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

232
00:12:35,670 --> 00:12:39,303
[LAUGHS]
- AHH.

233
00:12:40,236 --> 00:12:43,970
LOOK.
DO YOU SEE THIS?
- MM-HMM.

234
00:12:44,003 --> 00:12:49,370
IS THIS WHAT IT'S LIKE
TO BE HAPPY?

235
00:12:53,403 --> 00:12:55,403
[SNIFFS]

236
00:12:55,436 --> 00:12:58,570
- RIGHT HERE.
I'M SURE OF IT.

237
00:12:59,136 --> 00:13:03,603
IT'S FRESH, LIKE JUST BURIED.
[SCREAMS]

238
00:13:03,636 --> 00:13:08,670
[CRASH]
OH, MAN.
WHERE AM I?

239
00:13:08,703 --> 00:13:10,470
WHERE IS THIS?

240
00:13:10,503 --> 00:13:13,370
[GRUNTING]

241
00:13:30,803 --> 00:13:35,570
THEY'RE EGGS, AND SOMETHING
JUST HATCHED OUT OF THEM, TOO.

242
00:13:35,603 --> 00:13:37,536
THIS IS DEFINITELY THEIR NEST.

243
00:13:37,570 --> 00:13:39,903
- AAH!
UH-OH, NOW THAT THEY'RE HATCHED,

244
00:13:39,936 --> 00:13:42,803
THEIR PARENTS HAVE PROBABLY
TAKEN THEM OUT FOR TRAINING,

245
00:13:42,836 --> 00:13:46,770
AND TRAINING FOR WHAT?
EATING HUMANS, THAT'S WHAT.

246
00:13:46,803 --> 00:13:50,903
GIVING THE YOUNG
A TASTE FOR HUMAN FLESH.

247
00:13:50,936 --> 00:13:53,103
KAGOME'S IN DANGER.

248
00:13:57,270 --> 00:14:00,470
- MAYBE WE SHOULDN'T
- AH, DON'T TORTURE YOURSELF.

249
00:14:00,503 --> 00:14:01,803
THAT HALF-DEMON'S GOT IT COMING.

250
00:14:01,836 --> 00:14:04,570
- WHY SHOULD WE HAVE TO TRUST
ONE HALF-DEMON

251
00:14:04,603 --> 00:14:06,636
TO KILL ANOTHER, ANYWAY?

252
00:14:11,003 --> 00:14:14,736
- THIS FEELING.
I CAN'T EXPLAIN IT.

253
00:14:14,770 --> 00:14:18,270
BEING WITH HER,
I FEEL SO WARM.

254
00:14:18,303 --> 00:14:20,103
[SHOUTING]
- HUH?

255
00:14:20,136 --> 00:14:23,536
- COME ON.
YOU THINK WE DON'T KNOW
YOU KILLED THOSE PEOPLE?

256
00:14:23,570 --> 00:14:27,103
- NOBODY ASKED--
- THE VILLAGERS!

257
00:14:27,136 --> 00:14:28,536
- I KNOW IT.

258
00:14:28,570 --> 00:14:33,370
[WHIMPERING]
- IT'S OK.
STAY HERE.

259
00:14:33,403 --> 00:14:34,503
- UH--OH--OH!

260
00:14:34,536 --> 00:14:38,270
- HURT THIS OLD WITCH!
- WE LET YOU LIVE
NEAR US, TOO!

261
00:14:38,303 --> 00:14:41,436
- OW!
- HEY! THAT'S ENOUGH!

262
00:14:41,470 --> 00:14:43,203
- UH...

263
00:14:43,236 --> 00:14:45,303
- OH, NO.
ARE YOU GONNA BE OK?

264
00:14:45,336 --> 00:14:49,103
- MOVE, GIRL!
WHY ARE YOU PROTECTING THEM?

265
00:14:49,136 --> 00:14:51,903
- BECAUSE THEY HAVEN'T
DONE ANYTHING, THAT'S WHY,.

266
00:14:51,936 --> 00:14:54,370
WHICH YOU'D KNOW IF YOU WEREN'T
SO QUICK TO JUDGE.

267
00:14:54,403 --> 00:14:57,070
AND HOW CAN YOU ALL
BE SO MEAN TO HIM, ANYWAY?

268
00:14:57,103 --> 00:15:00,536
- DO YOU HEAR THAT?
SHE'S AS BAD AS THEM.
GET HER!

269
00:15:00,570 --> 00:15:04,303
- ANYONE WHO LOVES HALF-DEMONS
AS MUCH AS HER MUST BE ONE!

270
00:15:04,336 --> 00:15:06,003
I BET SHE'S GUILTY, TOO!

271
00:15:06,036 --> 00:15:08,603
- [SHOUTING]

272
00:15:09,336 --> 00:15:11,936
- OH, THE HUT!
- NO!

273
00:15:11,970 --> 00:15:13,770
[WHIMPERING]

274
00:15:13,803 --> 00:15:16,036
- YOU'VE GONE TOO FAR!

275
00:15:16,070 --> 00:15:18,636
[SCREAMING]

276
00:15:20,203 --> 00:15:24,070
- SOMEBODY HELP!
IT GOT ONE OF OUR GUYS!

277
00:15:24,103 --> 00:15:26,670
[SHOUTING]

278
00:15:26,703 --> 00:15:28,636
- THE YOUNG'UNS ARE
EATIN' ON HIM!

279
00:15:28,670 --> 00:15:30,903
- NEXT, THEY'LL EAT US!

280
00:15:30,936 --> 00:15:31,870
- DO YOU SEE?

281
00:15:31,903 --> 00:15:35,536
THERE'S YOUR FLESH-EATING
MONSTER RIGHT THERE.

282
00:15:37,670 --> 00:15:39,370
[SHOUTING]

283
00:15:39,403 --> 00:15:42,303
- I'VE GOTTA DO SOMETHING,
AND QUICK!

284
00:15:42,336 --> 00:15:44,870
[SHOUTING]

285
00:15:47,803 --> 00:15:51,570
JINENJI.
YOUR MOM NEEDS
YOUR HELP OUTSIDE.

286
00:15:51,603 --> 00:15:53,136
- HMM?

287
00:15:55,603 --> 00:15:58,036
HUH?
OH.

288
00:16:03,903 --> 00:16:06,203
- I GOT IT!

289
00:16:06,803 --> 00:16:09,070
[SCREAMS]

290
00:16:09,103 --> 00:16:10,903
UHH!

291
00:16:13,070 --> 00:16:15,603
[ROARING]

292
00:16:18,770 --> 00:16:20,736
[GROANING]

293
00:16:22,803 --> 00:16:24,970
[ROARING]

294
00:16:25,003 --> 00:16:27,670
[ROARING]

295
00:16:29,336 --> 00:16:31,936
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

296
00:16:31,970 --> 00:16:34,770
UGH!
- JINENJI!

297
00:16:36,336 --> 00:16:39,503
[GASP]
- JINENJI!

298
00:16:39,536 --> 00:16:40,970
- HEY!
GET AWAY!

299
00:16:41,003 --> 00:16:46,136
ONLY YOU EVER TREATED ME
LIKE A REAL PERSON.

300
00:16:46,170 --> 00:16:52,136
IF I LET YOU DIE HERE,
I WOULDN'T DESERVE
TO BE HALF-HUMAN.

301
00:16:52,170 --> 00:16:53,470
- JINENJI.

302
00:16:53,503 --> 00:16:55,670
- JINENJI!

303
00:16:55,703 --> 00:16:57,170
- UHH!

304
00:16:57,203 --> 00:16:57,903
- HYAH!

305
00:16:57,936 --> 00:17:00,070
- SOMEBODY HELP!
AAH!

306
00:17:00,103 --> 00:17:02,936
- IRON REAPER SOUL STEALER!

307
00:17:02,970 --> 00:17:05,270
KAGOME!
WHERE ARE YOU?

308
00:17:05,303 --> 00:17:09,203
- INUYASHA!
PLEASE HELP JINENJI!
[GROWLING]

309
00:17:09,236 --> 00:17:12,136
- WHATEVER--
- DON'T YOU DO IT!

310
00:17:12,170 --> 00:17:14,236
- WHAT?
- YOU MUSTN'T HELP HIM.

311
00:17:14,270 --> 00:17:17,636
JINENJI HAS TO LEARN
TO FIGHT FOR HIMSELF.

312
00:17:17,670 --> 00:17:20,370
- NOW?
[GROANING]

313
00:17:20,403 --> 00:17:24,236
- IT HAS TO BE NOW.

314
00:17:24,270 --> 00:17:26,870
[GROANING]

315
00:17:26,903 --> 00:17:28,603
- DON'T TELL ME YOU'RE LEAVING.

316
00:17:28,636 --> 00:17:31,903
AND HERE THE FUN
WAS JUST GETTING STARTED.

317
00:17:31,936 --> 00:17:33,670
WHO'S THE BIG COWARD NOW?

318
00:17:33,703 --> 00:17:36,336
- WE ARE, OK?
JUST DON'T HURT US.

319
00:17:36,370 --> 00:17:38,770
- YOU GOTTA HELP US.
WE'RE BEGGING HERE!

320
00:17:38,803 --> 00:17:40,870
- OH, I GET IT.

321
00:17:40,903 --> 00:17:44,136
WHOEVER'S STRONGEST IS
LEADER OF YOUR PACK, HUH?

322
00:17:44,170 --> 00:17:48,870
JINENJI!
SHOW THE COWARDS!
TEACH 'EM WHO'S BOSS!

323
00:17:48,903 --> 00:17:51,436
[ROARING]

324
00:17:58,814 --> 00:18:01,348
[ROARING]

325
00:18:02,281 --> 00:18:04,681
[GROWLING]

326
00:18:04,714 --> 00:18:07,014
[SHOUTING]

327
00:18:11,114 --> 00:18:14,014
[ROARING]

328
00:18:14,048 --> 00:18:16,581
[GROWLING]

329
00:18:18,681 --> 00:18:20,181
[ROARING

330
00:18:27,514 --> 00:18:29,381
- AMAZING!

331
00:18:34,114 --> 00:18:37,381
- NO!
[MUTTERING]

332
00:18:37,414 --> 00:18:41,314
- WELL, I GUESS IT'S BETTER
THEY LEARN LATE THAN NEVER.

333
00:18:41,348 --> 00:18:43,648
- DON'T YOU THINK THAT'S
OVERDOING IT A BIT?

334
00:18:43,681 --> 00:18:47,214
- HE'S GOTTA.
OTHERWISE, THEY'LL NEVER
RESPECT HIM.

335
00:18:47,248 --> 00:18:51,148
FAT CHANCE OF TEACHING
THESE MANGY DOGS NEW TRICKS.

336
00:18:51,181 --> 00:18:53,314
- I KNOW, BUT...

337
00:18:54,914 --> 00:18:58,081
- WE'RE SORRY.
- WE'RE--AAH!

338
00:18:58,114 --> 00:19:01,248
- PLEASE DON'T HURT US.
PLEASE.

339
00:19:01,281 --> 00:19:04,248
- IT'S JUST...
- HUH?

340
00:19:04,281 --> 00:19:04,914
HMM?

341
00:19:04,948 --> 00:19:06,548
- LOTS OF YOU ARE HURT.

342
00:19:06,581 --> 00:19:09,948
THIS WILL HELP YOU
GET BETTER FASTER.

343
00:19:09,981 --> 00:19:11,948
- THERE.
YOU SEE?

344
00:19:11,981 --> 00:19:14,114
- AND ALL THAT FOR NOTHING.

345
00:19:14,148 --> 00:19:16,148
- AHH!

346
00:19:17,448 --> 00:19:21,548
- YOU DIDN'T GET HURT,
DID YOU?

347
00:19:21,581 --> 00:19:23,781
- OH, JINENJI, YOU...

348
00:19:23,814 --> 00:19:25,248
- I KNOW.

349
00:19:25,281 --> 00:19:30,881
- IF THAT'S HOW THINGS ARE,
THAT'S HOW THEY'LL BE.

350
00:19:30,914 --> 00:19:33,548
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

351
00:19:34,748 --> 00:19:36,948
- YOU SURE YOU'LL BE OK?

352
00:19:36,981 --> 00:19:38,348
- OH, WE'LL BE FINE.

353
00:19:38,381 --> 00:19:42,381
YOU HURRY AND TAKE THAT MEDICINE
TO YOUR FRIEND, ALL RIGHT?

354
00:19:42,414 --> 00:19:46,448
- MM-HMM.
SEE YOU LATER, JINENJI.

355
00:19:47,248 --> 00:19:50,548
IT'S TIME FOR US TO LEAVE.
- OK.

356
00:19:50,581 --> 00:19:54,414
- THANK YOU, FOR EVERYTHING.

357
00:19:55,714 --> 00:19:56,448
- YOU'RE WELCOME.

358
00:19:56,481 --> 00:19:59,514
- MAYBE WE SHOULD BE
THANKING THEM.

359
00:19:59,548 --> 00:20:05,648
- OK, THAT'S ENOUGH OF THAT.
TOO MUCH WORK FOR TEARS.

360
00:20:05,681 --> 00:20:07,548
WHAT?
- HUH.

361
00:20:08,648 --> 00:20:10,748
- WE'LL HELP.

362
00:20:10,781 --> 00:20:12,548
- HUH?

363
00:20:15,381 --> 00:20:17,714
HAVE IT YOUR WAY.

364
00:20:19,548 --> 00:20:21,481
- SO.
- YEAH?

365
00:20:21,514 --> 00:20:24,981
- DID THAT KIND OF THING
HAPPEN TO YOU, TOO?

366
00:20:25,014 --> 00:20:26,914
- DID WHAT HAPPEN?

367
00:20:26,948 --> 00:20:30,248
- BULLYING.
WERE YOU PICKED ON?

368
00:20:30,281 --> 00:20:32,948
- HA.
YEAH, RIGHT.

369
00:20:32,981 --> 00:20:36,981
I DON'T ROLL OVER FOR ANYBODY.

370
00:20:37,014 --> 00:20:39,348
- NO.
OF COURSE NOT.

371
00:20:39,381 --> 00:20:42,748
MEANING, OF COURSE,
THAT HE WAS.

372
00:20:43,581 --> 00:20:44,948
- I'M NOT ONE OR THE OTHER.

373
00:20:44,981 --> 00:20:49,748
- HMM?
- NOT REALLY A DEMON,
NOT REALLY HUMAN.

374
00:20:49,781 --> 00:20:51,181
I'M NOT EITHER.

375
00:20:51,214 --> 00:20:54,481
THAT'S ALL.
THERE WAS NO PLACE FOR ME,

376
00:20:54,514 --> 00:20:56,448
SO I HAD TO MAKE ONE FOR MYSELF.

377
00:20:56,481 --> 00:20:59,614
AND THEN I REALIZED
I HAD A PLACE,

378
00:20:59,648 --> 00:21:01,414
BUT I WAS THE ONLY ONE IN IT.

379
00:21:01,448 --> 00:21:04,548
I DIDN'T KNOW ANY OTHER
WAY TO LIVE.

380
00:21:06,614 --> 00:21:10,348
- INUYASHA, I'M JUST...

381
00:21:11,181 --> 00:21:13,348
HAPPY TO HEAR IT.

382
00:21:13,381 --> 00:21:14,281
- HAPPY HOW?

383
00:21:14,314 --> 00:21:15,981
- WELL, IT'S JUST THAT
YOU'VE NEVER OPENED UP

384
00:21:16,014 --> 00:21:17,448
AND TALKED TO ME
LIKE THAT BEFORE.

385
00:21:17,481 --> 00:21:22,048
I'M GLAD YOU HAVE.
I'VE ALWAYS WONDERED
ABOUT YOUR PAST, YOU KNOW.

386
00:21:22,081 --> 00:21:25,614
I TOLD MYSELF YOU WERE
ALL BARK AND NO BITE,

387
00:21:25,648 --> 00:21:26,581
BUT I WASN'T SURE.

388
00:21:26,614 --> 00:21:30,781
I'M HAPPY YOU CAN TALK TO ME
SERIOUSLY, IS ALL.

389
00:21:30,814 --> 00:21:32,181
- AND THAT MAKES YOU HAPPY.

390
00:21:32,214 --> 00:21:36,014
- UH-HUH.
SO DON'T WORRY ABOUT
SHOWING ME YOUR SOFT SIDE, OK?

391
00:21:36,048 --> 00:21:40,348
- HA.
YOU MAKE IT SOUND LIKE
I'M SOME PET WHO NEEDS COMPANY.

392
00:21:40,381 --> 00:21:44,881
- WHAT'S WRONG WITH THAT?
IT'S NICE NOT TO BE ALONE.

393
00:21:45,514 --> 00:21:49,814
- IT'S TRUE.
I'M NOT ALONE, AM I?

394
00:21:49,848 --> 00:21:52,481
SOMEHOW, WITHOUT MY
EVER NOTICING IT,

395
00:21:52,514 --> 00:21:57,181
IT FELT SO NATURAL
HAVING KAGOME NEAR.

396
00:22:01,181 --> 00:22:04,914
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

397
00:23:38,345 --> 00:23:40,379
- A STRANGE MOUNTAIN
COVERED IN FOG.

398
00:23:40,412 --> 00:23:43,412
YOU CAN HEAR THE SCREAMS
ALL THE WAY AT THE BOTTOM.

399
00:23:43,445 --> 00:23:46,312
SOMETHING IS PULLING INUYASHA
TOWARD IT.

400
00:23:46,345 --> 00:23:49,745
SOMETHING MAKING DEMONS
STICK TOGETHER LIKE MAGNETS.

401
00:23:49,779 --> 00:23:52,079
IF INUYASHA KEEPS FIGHTING
LIKE THIS,

402
00:23:52,112 --> 00:23:53,812
HE'LL BE A PART OF IT TOO.

403
00:23:53,845 --> 00:23:57,745
KIKYO?
ARE YOU HERE TO HELP INUYASHA?

404
00:23:59,012 --> 00:24:00,579
NEXT TIME...

405
00:24:03,112 --> 00:24:04,112
SEE YOU SOON.

